org.jmisb.api.common

Class LogOnInvalidDataStrategy

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jmisb.api.common.LogOnInvalidDataStrategy
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IInvalidDataHandlerStrategy

    public class LogOnInvalidDataStrategy
extends Object
implements IInvalidDataHandlerStrategy
    Invalid data strategy that logs a warning message on invalid data.

    This is a good strategy to use for debugging and when handling data that is known to be non-compliant.
